        "translations": {
          "en": "Muhammad ibn al-Qasim al-Astarabadi (may Allah have mercy on him) narrated to us. He said: Ahmad ibn al-Hasan al-Husayni narrated to us, from al-Hasan ibn Ali ibn al-Nasir, from his father, from Muhammad ibn Ali, from his father al-Rida, from Musa ibn Ja'far (peace be upon them). He said: Al-Sadiq (peace be upon him) was asked about the ascetic in this world.",
